t Here》由 Chairlift 的 Patrick Wimberly、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/unknown-mortal-orchestra">Unknown Mortal Orchestra</a>贝斯手 Jacob Portrait 和合成流行音乐二人组<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/magdalena-bay">Magdalena Bay</a>制作。客座表演者包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daniel-caesar">Daniel Caesar</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foushee">Fousheé</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/teezo-touchdown">Teezo Touchdown</a> 、Justine Skye 和 Diana Gordon，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mac-demarco">Mac DeMarco</a>则被认为是两首歌曲《Drive Me Crazy!》的编剧。和“失败”。</p><p>这张专辑的灵感来自于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tame-impala">Tame Impala</a>的《Currents》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink-floyd">Pink Floyd</a>的开创性作品《Dark Side Of The Moon》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-ocean">Frank Ocean</a>的《Blonde》。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-yachty-lets-start-here-fuck-any-of-the-albums-i-dropped-before-this-one-3410547">“说实话，我一直不仅仅是嘻哈音乐，”</a>他在接受<em><a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/features/lil-yachty-lets-start-here-interview-sxsw-billboard-cover-story-1235281282/#recipient_hashed=87c91cb6f7c3bef8843b8e6fb6ffdcd835afd691d65df61a4fac92057c7f00dc&amp;recipient_salt=4ae5808f87b76ecdc83d2b728ac1c6c34add20ed3c6409345fd9815afa9fdc88" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Billboard</a></em>采访时说道。</p><p>他继续说道：“有很多孩子没有听过我的任何推荐。他们对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bon-iver">Bon Iver</a> 、平克·弗洛伊德、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">黑色安息日</a>或<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-brown">詹姆斯·布朗</a>一无所知。我想向人们展示我不同的一面——最重要的是我可以做任何事情。”</p><p></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-yachty-show-in-vancouver-pulled-midway-through-after-crowd-invited-to-rush-the-mosh-pit-3519300">温哥华的 Lil Yachty 秀结束后，受邀冲向 Mosh Pit 的人群</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
